            <lg xml:id="TK988">
<l>iṉmai yoruvaṟ kiḷivaṉṟu cālpeṉṉun </l>
<l>tiṇmaiyuṇ ṭākap peṟiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Poverty is no disgrace to one who abounds in good qualities.</l>
